description: More than two thirds of 94 migrants rescued in the Mediterranean test positive.
title: Coronavirus: Malta says 65 rescued migrants test positive
title_page: Coronavirus: Malta says 65 rescued migrants test positive - BBC News
maintext: "Migrants arriving by boat are immediately quarantined for 14 days and tested. The migrants who are positive will continue to be isolated and the rest will remain in quarantine and followed up," the health ministry said.
